node.text: Happy for ya @lukeprokop_ ! Sending my support 👊🏻

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Matt Duchene on July 13, 2021 tagging @ppr__. May be an image of 1 person, playing hockey and indoor.

node.text: Pekks… man, whatta career. I told you this in person when you told me you were retiring, and I truly mean it… I woulda given a lot to have played more years with you! Special teammate, special player, one of the BEST people I’ve ever met, period. Have an awesome retirement with Erika and sweet little Paulus and I can’t wait to see 35 raised to the Bridgestone rafters and watch you get inducted into the Hall of Fame. No one more deserving. Love ya pal, congrats @ppr__

node.text: Happy Anniversary to my beautiful wife! You are the best momma to our beautiful kids and the best friend and partner I could ever ask for. It’s fun doin’ life with you 😘 ❤️
